        {
          "title": "",
          "textContent": "We wish to make tourism in this mining locality so we prepared our inherited house for touristic accommodation. It is situated in the historical center and it had an important role in the community life, being used as a bank, medical center and later on even as a cinema. Today is a heritage building where we preserved the traditional style: the wooden floor, the doors, the windows or the heating with terracotta tiles. All around the house you can find our grandparents' old books, newspapers, magazines, that can be carefully read by the ones curious about them. <br>We offer <b>5% discount</b> to guests that bring their bikes and do at least one cycling track. It is not allowed to smoke inside or to listen loud music. <br><b>The booking will be confirmed by email or phone.</b>"
        }
      ]
